text: Ciecere Parish () is an administrative unit of Brocēni Municipality, Latvia. It was created in 2010 from the countryside territory of Brocēni town. At the beginning of 2014, the population of the parish was 1028. == Towns, villages and settlements of Ciecere parish == * Brocēnmuiža * Emburga * Lielciecere * Oškalni == References == Category:Parishes of Latvia Category:Brocēni Municipality
